channel.title: Reinforcement Worksheet: A Matter of Density
channel.description:
OK, so I have to find the density of some chemicals'.
And I wasn't paying attention in Science class, so I have no clue how.. Lol ):
Here is the information I'm given to find the density of the chemicals'.. I think that I have to find the density of each one.
[ul][li]a green liquid that has a volume of 48 L and a mass of 36 kg[/li] [li]a blue liquid that has a volume of 144 L and a mass of 129.6 kg[/li] [li]a red liquid that has a volume of 96 L and a mass of 115.2 kg[/li] [li]a black liquid that has a volume of 120 L and a mass of 96 kg[/li][/ul]
[b]NEED HELP ASAP![/b]
